* Create deployments
kubectl apply -f "name of yaml"

* View deployments
kubectl get deployment

* View pods
kubectl get pods

* Delete deployment
kubectl delete deployment "name of deploy"

* View services
kubectl get service

* Restart deployments
kubectl rollout restart deployment "name of deploy"

* View namespaces
kubectl get namespace

* View pods with namespaces
kubectl get pod --namespace="name of namespace"

* View services with namespaces
kubectl get service --namespace="name of namespace"


--> Installation loadbalancer nginx
kubectl apply -f https://raw.githubusercontent.com/kubernetes/ingress-nginx/controller-v1.0.0/deploy/static/provider/cloud/deploy.yaml
